        "content": "<p>I'd like to mark the important part of a tip in bold. We have several tips with 3-5 lines of text and I think marking the important parts is preferable compared to a uniform block of text. It also helps us think about what's important when writing the error. Anyone disagree?</p>\n<p>Example:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/_uJxVVb2ayOPmOQU3DwQuD08/Screenshot_20240729_195609.png\">type mismatch with tip</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/_uJxVVb2ayOPmOQU3DwQuD08/Screenshot_20240729_195609.png\" title=\"type mismatch with tip\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1069x566\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/22008/_uJxVVb2ayOPmOQU3DwQuD08/Screenshot_20240729_195609.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
